---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Digestive Harmony</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Digestive Harmony is a nonprofit dedicated to digestive health education, awareness, and community support." />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Digestive Health • Education • Community</p>
        <h1>Digestive Harmony</h1>
        <h2>Empowering better digestive health through education, awareness, and compassion.</h2>
        <p>
          Digestive Harmony is a nonprofit organization dedicated to helping individuals and families understand digestive conditions, find reliable resources, and feel supported on their health journey.
        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <a href="/about">Learn More</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="secondary">Explore Resources</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cards">
        <div>
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>To improve lives by providing trustworthy digestive health education and awareness.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Digestive Disorders</h3>
          <p>Learn about IBS, IBD, GERD, Crohn’s disease, ulcerative colitis, celiac disease, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Nutrition & Lifestyle</h3>
          <p>Practical guidance on gut-friendly food choices, wellness habits, and daily support.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Community Support</h3>
          <p>Helping patients, caregivers, and families feel informed, connected, and less alone.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #173b3f;
    background: #f4fbf9;
  }

  main {
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 90px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6f7f2, #ffffff);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #2c8c7c;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 64px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }

  .hero p {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .buttons a {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 8px;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #20796d;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .buttons .secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #20796d;
    border: 1px solid #20796d;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: auto;
  }

  .cards div {
    background: white;
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .cards h3 {
    color: #20796d;
  }

  .cards p {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 32px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
